<h3>Intruders</h3>
<div class="table datatable">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <!-- Entrance Point -->
            <h4>Entrance Point</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Shields, cannons, indestructible plating have no effect</li>
                <li>Thrusters connected to crew can be activated</li>
                <li>Red arrow & die roll determines entry point, either:
                    <ul>
                        <li>miss entirely - nothing happens</li>
                        <li>attempt to enter a defended tile - nothing happens, no reward</li>
                        <li>enter and begins moving through ship</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <!-- Movement -->
            <h4>Movement</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Use spare rocket to track position</li>
                <li>Count number of steps, with entry tile being 1</li>
                <li>Continue moving until reaching step limit OR encountering resistance</li>
                <li>Left-hand and right-hand rules</li>
                <li>Defeated when entering a defended tile - take reward</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <!-- Predators -->
            <h4>Predators</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Destroy crew, goods, batteries when entering tile</li>
                <li>Does not destroy:
                    <ul>
                        <li>hidden goods (support team)</li>
                        <li>hibernating astronauts in stasis chambers</li>
                        <li>armed crew - predator dies instead</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <!-- Commandos -->
            <h4>Commandos</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Move the indicated number of step(s) then plant charge(s)</li>
                <li>All planted charges will explode, even if commando is later destroyed</li>
                <li>Defended tiles destroy commando <i>before</i> he can plant a charge</li>
                <li>All charges explode simultaneously</li>
                <li>Multiple charges on the same tile is the same as a single charge there</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-12">
            <!-- Double Intruders -->
            <h4>Double Intruders</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Shared entry point; LHR for 1, RHR for the other</li>
                <li>Explode all bombs for double commando simultaneously</li>
                <li>Take reward for each defeated intruder</li>
                <li>A defended tile can stop both intruders</li>
                <li>Predator-commando plants bombs at intervals AND devours crew, goods, and batteries</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

<h3>Titles</h3>
<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>Replace "best-looking ship" rewards</li>
                <li>Randomly select N, return others to box</li>
                <li>Flight 1:
                    <ul>
                        <li>only finishing players can win a title</li>
                        <li>for each title, all players can earn $2 but only one gets the card; ties go to leading player</li>
                        <li>a player can earn multiple titles</li>
                        <li>if a player wins multiple, they only keep 1; give away the rest</li>
                        <li>if all players score 0, give title to lead player (but no money)</li>
                        <li>if no players finished, no one gets money, distribute titles randomly</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>Flight 2:
                    <ul>
                        <li><u>all</u> players will have a title, keep for entire game</li>
                        <li>defend title for $4:
                            <ul>
                                <li>finish without giving up</li>
                                <li>in first place for category (or tied)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>no money from other players' titles</li>
                        <li>keep title, even if failing to defend</li>
                        <li>flip to gold if successfully defend</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Flight 3:
                    <ul>
                        <li>defend silver title for $6</li>
                        <li>defend gold title for $12</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>


